fields.customfield_25665:
Please attach your DFD in the attachment field on the main tab. Requests submitted without a valid DFD will be automatically rejected.

DFD Intake Requirements

Acceptable format diagrams are:
Visio 2007 or higher
yED
Lucidchart

DFD Element Requirements:
Identify all known components in the application.
Display all Unicast and Multicast traffic flows.
Display all the IP protocol usage (tcp, udp, etc.)
Display all the Source and Destination ports.
Display the data sensitivity of each traffic flow.
Display all the traffic directions.

A good DFD will answer all of the following questions:
What is the flow requirement in bits per second from service to customer and what kind of traffic is it?
What is the flow requirement in bits per second between components and what kind of traffic is it?
What are the inter-data-center flow requirements?

fields.customfield_25665:
Please attach your DFD in the attachment field on the main tab. Requests submitted without a valid DFD will be automatically rejected.

DFD Intake Requirements

Acceptable format diagrams are:
Visio 2007 or higher
yED
Lucidchart

DFD Element Requirements:
Identify all known components in the application.
Display all Unicast and Multicast traffic flows.
Display all the IP protocol usage (tcp, udp, etc.)
Display all the Source and Destination ports.
Display the data sensitivity of each traffic flow.
Display all the traffic directions.

A good DFD will answer all of the following questions:
What is the flow requirement in bits per second from service to customer and what kind of traffic is it?
What is the flow requirement in bits per second between components and what kind of traffic is it?
What are the inter-data-center flow requirements?
